HEADWORD: Pilpul
<hw>Pil"pul</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Aramaic
<ets>pilp⟦umac⟧l</ets>; cf. Heb. <ets>pilpel</ets> to spice, to season,
